subsection.def:
building (建築物)
                means a building or structure constructed or adapted for use in accordance with a
                building plan;

building plan (建築圖則) means a plan—(a)approved by the Building Authority under the Buildings Ordinance;
                        or(b)prepared by the Hong Kong Housing Authority in relation to a building
                        to which the Buildings Ordinance does not apply under section
                            18(2) of the Housing Ordinance (Cap.
                            283);

